ption><option value="+81">+81</option><option value="+33">+33</option><option value="+86">+86</option></select><input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" class="w-3/4 px-4 py-2 border border-line rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required="" value=""/></div><textarea name="message" placeholder="Message" rows="4" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#ff6a00]"></textarea><button type="submit" class="w-full bg-green text-black py-3 text-lg rounded-lg font-semibold flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-red transition disabled:opacity-75">Submit</button></form></div></section><section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px) translateZ(0)"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="space-y-6"><details class="group rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.01] relative overflow-hidden" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) translateZ(0)"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="relative pl-6 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-1/2 before:-translate-y-1/2 before:w-2 before:h-2 before:rounded-full before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-orange-400 before:to-yellow-400"></span>How can I book a travel package?<span class="ml-2 text-orange-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300">⌄</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">You can book directly through our website or reach out to our travel experts for personalized assistance.</p></details><details class="group rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.01] relative overflow-hidden" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) translateZ(0)"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="relative pl-6 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-1/2 before:-translate-y-1/2 before:w-2 before:h-2 before:rounded-full before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-orange-400 before:to-yellow-400"></span>Do you offer group discounts?<span class="ml-2 text-orange-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300">⌄</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Yes! We offer special pricing and tailored itineraries for group bookings. Reach out to us to learn more.</p></details><details class="group rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.01] relative overflow-hidden" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) translateZ(0)"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="relative pl-6 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-1/2 before:-translate-y-1/2 before:w-2 before:h-2 before:rounded-full before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-orange-400 before:to-yellow-400"></span>Can I reschedule my trip?<span class="ml-2 text-orange-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300">⌄</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Absolutely. We offer flexible rescheduling policies based on availability and package terms.</p></details><details class="group rounded-xl bg-white shadow-md p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.01] relative overflow-hidden" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) translateZ(0)"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="relative pl-6 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-1/2 before:-translate-y-1/2 before:w-2 before:h-2 before:rounded-full before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-orange-400 before:to-yellow-400"></span>What payment methods do you accept?<span class="ml-2 text-orange-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300">⌄</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">We accept UPI, debit/credit cards, net banking, and EMI options through selected providers.</p></details></div></div></section><div class="px-6 pb-10" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px) translateZ(0)"><iframe class="w-full h-[300px] rounded-lg border" loading="lazy" referrerPolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><div id="footer" class="footer mt-0"><footer class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#102E50] to-[#000000] text-white pt-12" id="footer"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 pb-20"><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-blue-700"><div class="w-full md:w-1/4 text-center md:text-left"><a class="inline-block mb-4" href="/"><img alt="Travelxploria" loading="lazy" width="180" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mx-auto md:mx-0" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/images/logo-footer.png 1x, /images/logo-footer.png 2x" src="https://www.travelxploria.com/images/logo-footer.png"/></a><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm mt-2 md:mt-0">Travelxploria (unit of Explorer Club Holidays)</div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mt-2 md:mt-0"></div><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start gap-4 mt-6"><a class="text-[#ff886f] text-xl"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M13.397 20.997v-8.196h2.765l.411-3.209h-3.176V7.548c0-.926.258-1.56 1.587-1.56h1.684V3.127A22.336 22.336 0 0 0 14.201 3c-2.444 0-4.122 1.492-4.122 4.231v2.355H7.332v3.209h2.753v8.202h3.312z"></path></svg></a><a class="text-[#ff886f] text-xl"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0